{"about_the_game":"Take on the role of the A17 robot and you will discover the extraordinary secrets of a forgotten city. Build vehicles to reach the most distant, long-deserted places. Face numerous challenges, solve various puzzles and earn the most valuable rewards far beyond the borders of the safe district.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709530/extras/ExploreEnglish.png?t=1735316442\" /><br>Explore the extraordinary city, traversing the rooftops and ruins of buildings, discovering the secrets of a bygone world. Take on the role of a wanderer, make friends and defeat enemies to reach the furthest districts of the metropolis. Venture deeper and deeper, taking the risk of a path of no return and valuable rewards!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709530/extras/ExploreO.gif?t=1735316442\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709530/extras/BuildEnglish.png?t=1735316442\" /><br>Build machines to travel, fight and collect resources that make you the ultimate constructor. Express yourself with colors and paints. Upgrade your vehicles and conquer new territories by creating a perfect combat machine. Improve your vehicles with additional upgrades and gain new abilities!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709530/extras/BuildO.gif?t=1735316442\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709530/extras/ExperimentEnglish.png?t=1735316442\" /><br>Experiment with the acquired raw materials and parts to make the most of their potential. Discover the engineer within you by combining logical principles to obtain new effects of your machine. Create new more efficient vehicles with more parts. Take risks to survive. Search, discover, conqu